New Roman'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:0.1pt">to</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:0.1pt"> produce any evidence of having either the qualifications or experience to qualify their position.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:0.1pt">I suggest that instead of continuing your state sponsored persecution of </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:0.1pt">Sark</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:0.1pt"> Vineyards Ltd., you turn your attention to obtaining professional advice on the real environmental problems that people both on and off this Island are genuinely worried about, namely the indiscriminate burning of rubbish down at the </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:0.1pt">harbour</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:0.1pt"> which produces billowing clouds of toxic smoke, the dumping of the resulting toxic ash straight into the sea, the dumping of near-raw sewage over the cliff at Les </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:0.1pt">Laches</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:0.1pt">, the dumping of glass waste into the sea and, importantly, the complete absence of coherent safety precautions in handling asbestos’</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:0.1pt">Having obtained such professional advice, I suggest that you then act on it immediately</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:0.1pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size: